column2: SELECT TOP #  LTRIM(STR(mjd_r,#,#)) AS MJD,  dbo.fSDSS(p.objId) AS ID,  modelMag_g, modelMagErr_g,  modelMag_r, modelMagErr_r,  modelMag_i, modelMagErr_i, p.ra, p.dec  FROM detectionindex d   JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON d.objid=p.objid  JOIN Field f ON p.fieldid=f.fieldid WHERE p.ndetect > #
